{"tid":522284,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[仔傻係睇轉倒] 正能量whatsapp群","createTime":"2018-01-07T11:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T14:46:06.000Z","uid":73897,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1203dc138a882a2cb11af120d76743c85445b241","tid":522284,"uid":73897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:47:11.000Z","msg":"一世人流流長，總有迷失或者頹廢嘅時候。人冇咗目標，就冇咗前進嘅動力。好似條咬尾蛇噉唔知做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人生可能本無意義，意義可能就係要由我哋自己賦予。<br />\n<br />\n本群中指就係聚集喺塵世中嘅迷途小羔羊，一齊尋找苦海嘅明燈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人生入面嘅相遇係偶然，但總有其目的。<br />\n<br />\n好似你撳咗入蒞，睇到呢一行而冇即刻走，可能我哋就可以成為你人生中嘅幾位過客。雖然我哋未必為你帶蒞啲咩，但都可以當做一個經歷呀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個群就咩都講得嘅，前題係要健康。政治，社會，民生，日常生活on9無聊野，9up下都得，總會有人同你搭到嘴。<br />\n<br />\n說話講完，各位可以考慮下入蒞，睇下啱唔啱你 。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有性趣嘅巴絲可以填咗下面條link嘅google form，好快就會有專人聯絡你。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b24267369b74885f40a39b9df3f7b8a3ac7dcd","tid":522284,"uid":127788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T14:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624dbc868cfe86280b711d8fa0a5cedf0e1201cc","tid":522284,"uid":73897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T11:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec079e2484798650befcc4e21af0818a06a06431","tid":522284,"uid":73897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T14:14:13.000Z","msg":"儲多少少人一次過加<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0712545266883a72dd56fe9305e9edfa506a8304","tid":522284,"uid":127788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" cl